<p>A <b>Pyrrhic victory</b> (<small>IPA</small>: <span title="Pronunciation in IPA" class="IPA"><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:IPA_for_English" title="Wikipedia:IPA for English">/ˈpɪrɪk/</a></span>) is a victory with devastating cost to the victor.</p>
